            <div class="price" itemprop="price" content="24.99">
                <span class="main">24</span>
                <span class="price-details">
                    <span class="cents"><span itemprop="priceCurrency" content="EUR">€</span>99</span>
                    <span class="period">/mois</span>
                </span>
            </div>
            <!-- DOCUMENTATION --><br /><br /><!-- /DOCUMENTATION -->
            <div class="price is-main-price">
                <span class="main">24</span>
                <span class="price-details">
                    <span class="cents">€99</span>
                    <span class="period">/mois</span>
                </span>
            </div>
        {{/content}}

        {{#content "dark"}}
            <div class="price is-inverted">
                <span class="main">24</span>
                <span class="price-details">
                    <span class="cents">€99</span>
                    <span class="period">/mois</span>
                </span>
            </div>
        {{/content}}

        {{#content "do"}}
            <p><em>Voir l'exemple ci-dessus</em></p>
            <ul class="list">
                <li>Pour la couleur de la marque, utilisez la classe <strong class="has-text-primary">.is-main-price</strong>.</li>
                <li>Lorsqu'un prix se trouve dans un bloc à fond coloré, alors il faut lui ajouter la classe <strong class="has-text-primary">.is-inverted</strong>, le prix deviendra alors blanc.</li>
            </ul>
        {{/content}}
    {{/snippet}}
</section>

